Class ContinuousMeasure

  • java.lang.Object
    • smile.data.measure.ContinuousMeasure

    public abstract class ContinuousMeasure
extends java.lang.Object
implements Measure
    Continuous data are numerical data that can theoretically be measured in infinitely small units. The statistical analysis of continuous data is more powerful than that of categorical data.
